Package: bayesVG
Type: Package
Title: Identify Variable Genes via Bayesian Inference
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: c(person(given = c("Jack", "R."), family = "Leary", email = "j.leary@ufl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-8821-3269")))
Description: Our method implements efficient highly and spatially variable gene identification in scRNA-seq and spatial transcriptomics data using approximate Bayesian hierarchical models.
